### 3. New Phase Detectors
**[MODIFY]** [phases.py](file:///Users/traftonobrien/Desktop/pitch-tracker/src/mechanics/phases.py)

| Phase | Detection Method |
|---|---|
| **most_loaded** | Composite: lead knee at lowest y + maximum hip hinge angle (shoulder→hip→knee), between PLL and FS |
| **foot_strike** (refined) | Full foot plant: both HEEL and FOOT_INDEX velocity stable simultaneously after descent. Falls back to original ankle velocity method |
| **weight_bearing** | Hip midpoint x-position closest to lead ankle x-position, after foot strike |
| **arm_flip_up** | Forearm angle ≥45° above horizontal AND wrist above shoulder |

### 4. PitchPhases Dataclass Expansion

